02:19.240 --> 02:21.240
Any of you.

02:21.242 --> 02:24.910
I'm in charge here,
and I say it's your fault.

02:24.912 --> 02:26.578
Obviously,

02:26.580 --> 02:28.580
No one's coming to the show

02:28.582 --> 02:30.916
Because you are boring.

02:30.918 --> 02:32.417
The town has had their fill

02:32.419 --> 02:33.752
Of your mediocre

02:33.754 --> 02:36.588
Oddities.

02:36.590 --> 02:37.756
The thrill is gone.

02:37.758 --> 02:40.125
You're yesterday's news.

02:40.127 --> 02:42.094
