attractive on you.

02:56.944 --> 02:58.443
Don't you touch her.

02:58.445 --> 03:00.112
This is my show!
I'll do whatever I want!

03:00.114 --> 03:01.346
That's is, mister.

03:03.116 --> 03:05.517
(groans)

03:06.953 --> 03:08.620
