03:08.622 --> 03:11.957
I was willing to eat shit
to keep this place going,

03:11.959 --> 03:14.793
But I'd rather starve
than listen to your whiny voice

03:14.795 --> 03:16.528
One more time.

03:16.530 --> 03:18.130
No one wants

03:18.132 --> 03:19.965
To see some pretentious prick

03:19.967 --> 03:21.967
