03:21.969 --> 03:25.304
And no one gives a shit
about bloody cole porter.

03:25.306 --> 03:27.005
Hey.
You think you're special.

03:27.007 --> 03:29.975
Your mum probably told you
all your life.

03:29.977 --> 03:32.077
Well, I've got news for you.

03:32.079 --> 03:34.079
