03:37.751 --> 03:39.318
You're boring.

03:39.320 --> 03:40.586
(laughter)

03:40.588 --> 03:42.754
And we don't trade
in boring.

03:42.756 --> 03:45.824
We're freaks.

03:45.826 --> 03:48.260
