have talked about this.

20:17.650 --> 20:20.218
We both agree you should
have your privacy.

20:25.090 --> 20:28.326
It's an old trick, I've been
doing it since we were little.

20:28.328 --> 20:30.161
I just leave my body.

20:31.597 --> 20:33.097
Well, I'd like to think

20:33.099 --> 20:35.600
You'd want to join us,
from time to time...

20:35.602 --> 20:37.168
In our revels.

20:38.437 --> 20:40.438
