at the table with us.

22:26.446 --> 22:28.512
I ain't no maid.

22:29.781 --> 22:32.283
Mm, ring any bells?

22:32.285 --> 22:34.452
I know we all
look alike to you.

22:34.454 --> 22:36.287
What's going on?

22:36.289 --> 22:37.621
